18:27.976 --> 18:31.371
MY FIRM REPRESENTS THE
OWNERS OF THE SAN DIMAS PIER.

18:33.416 --> 18:35.418
-THE BAD GUYS, AS IT WERE.

18:35.549 --> 18:37.333
-IT'S NOT THAT
CUT AND DRIED, KAY.

18:37.464 --> 18:39.248
-NOT NOW IT ISN'T, NO.

18:39.379 --> 18:41.381
NOT WITH THE TWO OF
US GOING HEAD-TO-HEAD.

18:41.511 --> 18:43.296
