RATHER STICKY.

18:43.426 --> 18:45.559
-HEY, WAIT A MINUTE. I'M NOT
ASKING YOU TO KILL THE STORY.

18:45.689 --> 18:47.648
-GOOD BECAUSE I WON'T.

18:47.778 --> 18:49.693
