7HEY, DIDN'T I SEND YOU A
POSTCARD FROM THAILAND?

19:18.635 --> 19:20.289
-OH, YEAH.

19:20.420 --> 19:21.986
UM, I THINK I TOOK IT TO
SHOW AND TELL FOR SCHOOL.

19:23.205 --> 19:24.859
-THAILAND IS AN UNREAL PLACE.

19:24.989 --> 19:29.342
THE SURF IS LAME, BUT THE
CHICKS ARE AWESOME, DUDE.

19:29.472 --> 19:31.213
[LAUGHS]

19:31.344 --> 19:32.997
-CAN I HAVE SOME MORE COKE?

19:36.827 --> 19:37.654
-HEY, CAN I HAVE SOME?

19:38.568 --> 19:40.353
-NO. FINISH YOUR MILK.

19:41.658 --> 19:42.746
-KYLE GETS COKE.

19:43.660 --> 19:46.010
-COME ON, A LITTLE
SODA? HERE YOU GO, HOBIE.

19:47.882 --> 19:48.796
-BUZZ.

19:48.926 --> 19:50.493
-WHAT, DAD?

19:51.059 --> 19:52.930
I MEAN, LISTEN TO YOURSELF.
THAT'S WHO YOU SOUND LIKE.

19:53.453 --> 19:55.194
DON'T DO THIS, DON'T DO THAT.

19:55.977 --> 19:58.849
YOU GOT A RULE FOR
EVERYTHING. LIGHTEN UP, BRAH.

19:58.980 --> 20:00.634
-WHY DON'T YOU SHUT UP?

20:10.644 --> 20:11.427
ANYBODY WANT ANYMORE CHICKEN?

20:11.558 --> 20:12.733
-NO, NO. I'M DONE.

20:14.082 --> 20:15.431
-HEY, BUZZ. GOT ANY BREAD?

20:15.562 --> 20:17.216
WE'RE GONNA GO
CRUISE THE STRAND.

20:18.347 --> 20:19.435
-WAIT A MINUTE.

20:20.001 --> 20:22.221
WHAT DO YOU MEAN WE'RE
GONNA GO CRUISE THE STRAND?

20:23.265 --> 20:24.484
-WE'LL BE HOME BEFORE CURFEW.

20:24.614 --> 20:26.007
-DON'T EVEN THINK IT.

20:26.747 --> 20:28.923
-WHAT IS THIS, SOME KIND
OF JAIL OR SOMETHING?

20:29.053 --> 20:31.404
-HEY, KYLE, SLOW DOWN.

20:32.100 --> 20:33.710
I HAPPEN TO AGREE ON THIS ONE.

20:33.841 --> 20:35.495
I READ WHERE THERE'S SOME
GANG SHOOTINGS DOWN THERE.

20:36.017 --> 20:39.063
-HEY, BUZZ, MAYBE YOU'LL GET
LUCKY. MAYBE I'LL GET SHOT.

20:39.934 --> 20:43.198
-KYLE. HEY, KYLE,
WAIT A MINUTE, MAN!

20:44.895 --> 20:45.722
-CAN I BE EXCUSED?

20:45.853 --> 20:46.897
-GO ON.

20:50.901 --> 20:53.556
-WELL, AS YOU CAN SEE, WE
HAVEN'T EXACTLY BONDED YET.

20:55.254 --> 20:56.864
-THINGS ARE MOVING A LITTLE
FAST FOR HIM, THAT'S ALL.

20:56.994 --> 20:59.301
-[SCOFFS] YEAH,
FOR THE BOTH OF US.

21:00.563 --> 21:02.391
TALK ABOUT GOING
THROUGH SOME CHANGES.

21:02.522 --> 21:04.088
ONE DAY I'M SITTING ON
THE BEACH IN AUSTRALIA,

21:04.219 --> 21:06.177
THE NEXT DAY I'M
SOME ANGRY KID'S DAD.

21:07.527 --> 21:09.746
NO, IT WAS NOT SUPPOSED
TO HAPPEN LIKE THIS.

21:09.877 --> 21:12.967
-SO YOU MAKE A FEW
ADJUSTMENTS. THAT'S LIFE, BUZZ.

21:14.925 --> 21:16.927
THE GREAT MYSTERY
TO BEING A FATHER, ANYWAY.

21:18.538 --> 21:20.714
A LOT OF COMMON SENSE, INSTINCT.

21:20.844 --> 21:23.282
YOU KNOW, REMEMBERING HOW
MOM AND DAD HANDLED THINGS.

21:23.412 --> 21:25.675
-YEAH, THEN DO EVERYTHING
EXACTLY THE OPPOSITE.

21:26.415 --> 21:28.330
-OH, YOU KNOW, WHY DON'T
YOU LEAVE THEM ALONE?

21:29.375 --> 21:31.072
THEY DIDN'T MAKE YOU LEAVE HOME.

21:31.202 --> 21:33.161
-HEY, I LEFT HOME BECAUSE
I DIDN'T BELIEVE IN THE WAR.

21:33.814 --> 21:36.643
THAT'S WHY. AND HE'S
NEVER FORGIVEN ME FOR IT.

21:43.389 --> 21:44.781
-WHAT GROUPS YOU INTO?

21:44.912 --> 21:46.914
-WELL, I DON'T HAVE
ANY REAL FAVORITES.

21:49.090 --> 21:52.267
-NEW KIDS ON THE BLOCK?
MAN, WHAT A BARNEY.

21:52.963 --> 21:53.790
-WHAT'S A BARNEY?

21:54.748 --> 21:56.402
-A GEEK.
-HOBIE: OH.

21:57.751 --> 21:58.839
-YOU EVER LISTEN TO THE DEAD?

21:59.448 --> 22:01.494
-HOBIE: THE WHO?
-THE GRATEFUL DEAD.

22:02.451 --> 22:04.105
THEY WERE MY MOM'S
FAVORITE GROUP.

22:05.846 --> 22:07.891
I MEAN, SHE TOOK ME TO
A LOT OF THEIR CONCERTS.

22:08.457 --> 22:11.242
IT'S LIKE ALL THESE OLD
HIPPIES. MAN, WHAT A TRIP.

22:13.549 --> 22:15.290
-HOW DID YOUR MOM DIE?

22:15.421 --> 22:17.988
I MEAN, IF YOU DON'T WANT TO
TALK ABOUT IT, THAT'S OKAY.

22:18.119 --> 22:19.425
-NO, NO, THAT'S ALL RIGHT.

22:20.469 --> 22:22.341
I MEAN, I DREAM
ABOUT IT EVERY NIGHT.

22:24.343 --> 22:26.823
SHE, UH, SHE WAS RIDING HER BIKE

22:28.390 --> 22:30.305
AND THIS CAR
CRASHED A STOP SIGN.

22:32.089 --> 22:33.352
NEVER EVEN SLOWED DOWN.

22:34.222 --> 22:37.834
JUST, IT WAS JUST LIKE, POW.

22:41.316 --> 22:44.580
SHE, UH, SHE WENT
STRAIGHT UP IN THE AIR.

22:47.322 --> 22:48.758
CAME DOWN RIGHT
ON THE WINDSHIELD.

22:49.280 --> 22:50.369
-YOU SAW IT?

22:56.766 --> 22:58.246
-I WAS RIGHT BEHIND HER.

23:03.207 --> 23:04.687
I SAW THE CAR.

23:06.167 --> 23:07.124
I YELLED.

23:09.605 --> 23:10.867
