23:43.247 --> 23:44.597
-OKAY, ALL RIGHT. JUST RELAX.

23:44.727 --> 23:45.554
-OH, GOD.

23:45.685 --> 23:46.642
-CALM DOWN.

23:52.300 --> 23:53.301
-EDUARDO!

23:53.432 --> 23:54.650
