24:27.640 --> 24:28.554
-WHAT'S GOIN' ON?

24:29.511 --> 24:31.426
-EDUARDO'S SUITS
ARE DISINTEGRATING.

24:31.557 --> 24:32.514
-WHAT?

24:32.645 --> 24:34.385
-YEAH.
-SHAUNI: OH, GOD.

24:34.516 --> 24:35.952
[CROWD CHEERING AND CLAPPING]

24:36.083 --> 24:37.911
HEY, YOU TELL EDUARDO
I WANNA TALK TO HIM!

24:38.520 --> 24:39.826
-YEAH, WELL, TAKE A NUMBER.

24:41.392 --> 24:43.438
-MY WIFE SAID YOU WERE
SELLING THOSE BIKINIS.

24:43.569 --> 24:45.788
-OH, I'M SORRY, BUT
THEY'RE ALL GONE. SOLD OUT.

24:45.919 --> 24:47.573
PERHAPS NEXT WEEK.

24:47.703 --> 24:49.966
-YEAH, WELL, SHE WANTS HER
MONEY BACK, AND SO DO I.

24:50.576 --> 24:51.838
AS A MATTER OF FACT,
WE ALL DO.

24:52.360 --> 24:54.188
-WELL, UH, THERE'S A
SLIGHT PROBLEM WITH THAT.

24:54.318 --> 24:58.758
YOU SEE, ALL SALES ARE FINAL.
OH, IT'S A VERY STRICT POLICY.

24:59.846 --> 25:01.848
BUT SEEING AS HOW WE'RE
SO CLOSE TOGETHER,

25:01.978 --> 25:04.154
MAYBE I CAN GIVE YOU
A PARTIAL REFUND.

25:04.285 --> 25:05.242
