ARE PUMPING. LET'S GO OUT.

25:29.092 --> 25:30.920
-I CAN'T. I GOT
JUNIOR LIFEGUARD.

25:31.573 --> 25:32.661
-OH, MAN, BAIL IT.

25:32.792 --> 25:33.706
-I CAN'T.

25:35.359 --> 25:37.971
-MAN, THAT'S WEAK. YOUR DAD
MAKES YOU DO ALL THIS STUFF?

25:38.667 --> 25:41.148
-NO, I LIKE IT. IT'S FUN.
BESIDES, YOU LEARN A LOT.

25:41.844 --> 25:43.411
-YEAH, LIKE HOW TO BE A BARNEY.

25:43.977 --> 25:45.761
LOOK, MAN, ALL I CAN SAY
IS YOU'RE GOING TO MISS OUT

25:45.892 --> 25:46.936
ON SOME GNARLY WAVES.

25:47.589 --> 25:48.459
-WHERE YOU GOING?

25:48.590 --> 25:50.331
-SAN DIMAS PIER.

25:50.461 --> 25:53.029
MET SOME DUDE, SAID THEY WERE
THE HAIRIEST BREAK AROUND.

25:53.813 --> 25:55.379
-YOU CAN'T SURF THERE
IT'S TOO DANGEROUS.

25:55.510 --> 25:57.556
-NOT FOR ME. LATER.

25:58.861 --> 26:00.733
-WAIT UP, KYLE! I'M COMIN'.

